{"tid":478400,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本超級美女？　真相係40歲偽娘大叔！","createTime":"2017-11-24T04:42:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-24T09:47:43.000Z","uid":3189,"like":15,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"c88c1fb7fb8a57a04ad7cedbac1f599c62fe6255","tid":478400,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T04:42:32.000Z","msg":"11月21日(二) 05:23<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20171121/photo/bknint-20171121052303715-1121_17011_001_01p.jpg?20171121120224\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171121%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20171121052303715-1121_17011_001_01p.jpg%3F20171121120224&h=f1d3b875&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n谷琢磨與女兒的合照（左）引起熱話。（互聯網圖片）<br />\n<br />\n日本歌手谷琢磨，乍看是一位樣子甜美、正值年輕的少女，但事實上卻讓人大吃一驚，皆因「他」是一名年屆40、已婚並育有一名女兒的叔叔。這位單憑外貌定會讓人誤會性別的「偽娘」，近日在其Twitter上抱着女兒合照，相中卻以可愛字體寫上「祝父親40歲生日快樂」，讓發現真相的網民不禁高呼「詐騙」，一時間成為網絡熱話。<br />\n<br />\n谷琢磨於上周五（17日）剛好40歲，故於Twitter上公布與女兒的合照，並留言指本年喜獲愛女、成為父親，是人生中的一個里程碑。不過，其附上的照片才是眾人的熱議對象，皆因谷琢磨綁起雙馬尾、身穿蕾絲花邊裙裝，令人懷疑「他」是媽媽才對。該張相片目前已獲逾1.6萬人轉推，逾2萬人讚好。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，谷琢磨的身高僅有162cm，體重更只得47公斤，身型看起來更像女性。他於2005年起，在歌謠搖滾樂隊「實驗台天竺鼠」擔任主音歌手，穿女裝的契機是2011年時，有雜誌的女模特兒突然缺席，結果被拜託頂替。從此之後，即使在舞台上表演，他亦如覺醒般一直男扮女裝。更令人難以置信的是，谷琢磨於2015年更新駕照，竟順利以女裝照片通過，獲得「國家承認」。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民得悉谷琢磨背後的「真相」後，不能相信事實如此「殘酷」，有人驚呼「怎麼可能是40歲的大叔！」，亦有人留言表示「皮膚比20多歲的我還要好！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20171121/photo/bknint-20171121052303715-1121_17011_001_02p.jpg?20171121120224\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171121%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20171121052303715-1121_17011_001_02p.jpg%3F20171121120224&h=a9cd115d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網民難以相信谷琢磨是男性。（互聯網圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20171121/photo/bknint-20171121052303715-1121_17011_001_03p.jpg?20171121120224\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171121%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20171121052303715-1121_17011_001_03p.jpg%3F20171121120224&h=28e8747a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n谷琢磨以女裝更新駕照獲得通過。（互聯網圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20171121/photo/bknint-20171121052303715-1121_17011_001_04p.jpg?20171121120224\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171121%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20171121052303715-1121_17011_001_04p.jpg%3F20171121120224&h=19f0430d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n谷琢磨的男性打扮。（互聯網圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20171121/bknint-20171121052303715-1121_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171121%2Fbknint-20171121052303715-1121_17011_001.html&d=SMktEMoWLNgn8ZGgHr2NV0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=1fe8e2da\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20171121/bknint-20171121052303715-1121_17011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"2809fd5fdf6a32a22cef4e72799291c6ef140c05","tid":478400,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T04:44:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a050e78117e884327b5327ccc26fc93d861a477","tid":478400,"uid":17081,"like":113,"dislike":0,"score":113,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T04:57:22.000Z","msg":"You竟然是個uncle<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63475d8ef70d025626536c3c1a5de06990e66eb7","tid":478400,"uid":19979,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T05:00:31.000Z","msg":"父女丼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af48abed406f935c9da693f17d8bc0451fbd852f","tid":478400,"uid":145117,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T05:03:13.000Z","msg":"男性打扮都成個女人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"934078bc4d68006fe3ded9b306d1a20c6a11911a","tid":478400,"uid":40940,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"re